					<h4>
						<a style="color:black" href="#">
							Checkers is a FMCG retailer owned by Shoprite that operates in Southern Africa.
							Checkers currently has 37 Checkers Hypers and 202 Checkers supermarkets operating in Botswana, South Africa and Namibia
